### Standard Favicon Links

```html
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
```

**Description:**
Favicons are small icons that appear in the browser tab, bookmarks, and address bar.
You can link them manually using the `<link>` tag.

* Use the MIME type `image/png` for **PNG** files.
* Use the MIME type `image/x-icon` for **ICO** files.

These types help browsers correctly identify and render the favicon format.
